channel.title: Comments on: Equipment Review: Rosewood Go Bowls with Carved Orchids

item.title: By: Ben
item.dc:creator: Ben
item.description: To be honest, I don't see anything official on the website; but based on the ones I have, the art seems to be organic and hand-done as opposed to a computer print carving. (If you pay attention to the characters on the lid, they are different sizes.) I could be wrong though! =)
